_sText: This is my second map I made so far, I will be working on V2 next week. Theres two ways you can play this map, you can fight between your spawns or you can Bomb & Defuse. The bombsites don't look much but my maps will get better and better as I practice. Also there are some shortcuts to get to bombsites quickly and stealthily. This map can play 32 players.
